appShortcutName: WhatsApp Web To Go - Mobile Client for WhatsApp We
appDisplayName: WhatsApp Web To Go - Mobile Client for WhatsApp We
description: Access WhatsApp Web on your mobile device - send pictures, audio and video WhatsApp Web To Go lets you access WhatsApp Web on your mobile phone or tablet. It has full support for sending pictures, audio and video - with a clean and easy interface. Free and without ads. If you have problems, just send a mail or create a GitHub issue. This app is in no way affiliated with WhatsApp Inc. The rights for WhatsApp and WhatsApp Web belong to WhatsApp Inc. This app is a private project to enable the use of WhatsApp Web on Android devices.
